modName: Dragonbone Ebony Armor Retexture HD and 4K WIP
descriptionHtml:
Got asked to improve the Ebonsteel dragonbone armor.
The set uses some parts of the vanilla texture, so I ported some of my stuff over to this armor.
As the other mod is only at 50%, this is around at 5%
Later on I will improve the whole armor set.

You need the main mod, overwrite with my files.
